.SH NAME
App::My::PandocUpdateTemplates::FilepathMapping \- model a mapping between repo and stow files
.SH VERSION
.IX Header "VERSION"
This documentation is for App::My::PandocUpdateTemplates::FilepathMapping
version 0.1.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 4
\&    use Moo;
\&    use Const::Fast;
