.SH DESCRIPTION
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
This is an accessory module for App::My::PandocUpdateTemplates::Update that
models a downloaded repository files and its corresponding stow package
templates directory file.
.SH "CONFIGURATION AND ENVIRONMENT"
.IX Header "CONFIGURATION AND ENVIRONMENT"
.SS Properties/attributes
.IX Subsection "Properties/attributes"
\fIdownloaded_file_path\fR
.IX Subsection "downloaded_file_path"
.PP
The path to a downloaded file from an online repository.
.PP
A Types::Path::Tiny::AbsPath object, which can accept a Path::Tiny
object. Required.
.PP
\fIstow_file_path\fR
.IX Subsection "stow_file_path"
.PP
The path to a stow package file that maps to the downloaded repository file
defined in the "downloaded_file_path" attribute.
.PP
A Types::Path::Tiny::AbsPath object, which can accept a Path::Tiny
object. Required.
